The paper deals with decision-making under uncertainty and optimization, which are core topics in game theory (cs.GT), data structures (cs.DS), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and information theory (cs.IT). The problem formulation involves online decision-making, which is a common theme in these subfields.
